# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible — never ship host artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
.git
.github
**/*.log
# Secrets come from the host's env vars at runtime, never baked into the image.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
# Not needed by the backend image.
frontend/.next
design
design-system
docs
